 <label class="label">Figure 3</label>
 <caption class="caption">
  <p class="p">(a) Map of the Representative Concentration Pathway 4.5 (RCP4.5) multimodel mean (MMM) value of 
   <math id="nlm-math-1" class="math">
    <mi class="mi">ξ</mi>
    <mo class="mo">=</mo>
    <mfrac class="mfrac">
     <mrow class="mrow">
      <msub class="msub">
       <mi class="mi">m</mi>
       <mi class="mi">max</mi>
      </msub>
      <mo class="mo">−</mo>
      <msub class="msub">
       <mi class="mi">m</mi>
       <mi class="mi">end</mi>
      </msub>
     </mrow>
     <mi class="mi">ϵ</mi>
    </mfrac>
    <mo class="mo">,</mo>
   </math> where 
   <inline-formula class="inline-formula">
    <styled-content style="italic-in-any-context" class="styled-content">m</styled-content>
    <sub class="sub">max</sub>
   </inline-formula> is the 21st century maximum MMM warming rate, 
   <inline-formula class="inline-formula">
    <styled-content style="italic-in-any-context" class="styled-content">m</styled-content>
    <sub class="sub">end</sub>
   </inline-formula> is the 23rd century MMM warming rate, and 
   <inline-formula class="inline-formula">
    <styled-content style="italic-in-any-context" class="styled-content">ϵ</styled-content>
   </inline-formula> is the multimodel standard deviation of 
   <inline-formula class="inline-formula">
    <styled-content style="italic-in-any-context" class="styled-content">m</styled-content>
    <sub class="sub">end</sub>
   </inline-formula>. (b) Map of the RCP4.5 MMM value of 
   <inline-formula class="inline-formula">
    <styled-content style="italic-in-any-context" class="styled-content">m</styled-content>
    <sub class="sub">end</sub>
   </inline-formula> in degrees Celsius per decade. (c) Map of the Coupled Model Intercomparison Project Phase 5 RCP4.5 MMM value of 
   <inline-formula class="inline-formula">
    <styled-content style="italic-in-any-context" class="styled-content">ϵ</styled-content>.
   </inline-formula> (d) Map of the RCP4.5 MMM value of 
   <math id="nlm-math-2" class="math">
    <mfrac class="mfrac">
     <msub class="msub">
      <mi class="mi">m</mi>
      <mi class="mi">end</mi>
     </msub>
     <msub class="msub">
      <mi class="mi">m</mi>
      <mi class="mi">max</mi>
     </msub>
    </mfrac>
    <mo class="mo">.</mo>
   </math>
  </p>
 </caption>
